@startuml
title Course Enrollment And Lesson Progression

actor Student
participant "Offers Page\npages/offres.php" as OffersPage
participant "Enrollment Action" as EnrollAction
participant "My Courses\npages/cours.php" as CoursesPage
participant "Lessons Page" as LessonsPage
participant "Validate Lesson" as ValidateAction
database "MySQL DB" as DB

Student -> OffersPage: Open available offers
OffersPage --> Student: Show free and premium offers

alt Free course path
    Student -> EnrollAction: Send free enrollment request
    EnrollAction -> DB: Save enrollment
    EnrollAction --> CoursesPage: Redirect to my courses
else Premium course path
    Student -> EnrollAction: Confirm payment
    EnrollAction -> DB: Save paid enrollment
    EnrollAction --> CoursesPage: Redirect to my courses
end

CoursesPage -> DB: Load enrolled courses
DB --> CoursesPage: Student course dashboard
Student -> LessonsPage: Open one course
Student -> ValidateAction: Mark lesson as completed
ValidateAction -> DB: Save lesson progress
ValidateAction --> LessonsPage: Return updated lesson list

@enduml
